            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股四巫日窄幅  科技股受壓  Circle再飆兩成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周五為美股「四期結算日」(Quadruple witching day，四巫日)，美股窄幅，美國總統特朗普暗示暫緩對伊朗的攻擊行動，紓緩市場緊張情緒，聯儲局官員發表減息言論。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_24225396675297.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_24225396675297.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">四巫日即指數及個別股份的期貨和期權結算日，涉及到期合約價值達6.5萬億美元，根據過往紀錄，該日市況一般較為波動，不過周五的市況較為平靜。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_24225396675297.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_24225396675297.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：台積電官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/bplib_20250417-111635_20250317_GL_Apple-Watch-10_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/bplib_20250417-111635_20250317_GL_Apple-Watch-10_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_24225396675297.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：台積電官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/bplib_20250417-111635_20250317_GL_Apple-Watch-10_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數收市報42206點，升35點或0.08%，高開119點後，升幅擴大至最多260點，高見42432點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數報19447點，跌98點，曾漲0.77%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數報5967點，跌13點，一度回升0.62%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克金龍中國指數收跌0.92%，報7126.70點，本周累跌1.48%，周一上漲，隨後持續回落。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">憧憬穩定幣發展前景，穩定幣發行商Circle Internet再大幅炒高20.39%，連升兩天，創上市新高。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">費城半導體指數收跌0.75%，報5211.48點。據《華爾街日報》消息表示，一位美國官員通知台積電等半導體公司，計劃取消允許它們在中國使用美國技術的豁免。台積電ADR跌1.87%，本周累計下跌0.75% ; AMD漲1.14%。芯片設備制造商應用材料公司股價收跌1.96%，荷蘭阿斯麥控股公司下跌0.67%。Nvidia跌1.12%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：台積電官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250417_FI_source-web_TSMC-3-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：台積電官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科技股拖累大市，Meta宣布推出與Oakley聯乘的人工智能(AI)智能眼鏡，售價399美元起，股價先升後跌1.9%。亞馬遜與輝達跌幅都超過1%，Alphabet挫3.9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">彭博報道，特斯拉將於7月在印度開設首家陳列室，正式進軍這個全球第三大汽車市場，股價一度抽高3.2%，收市幾乎持平。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蘋果公司收市股價反彈2.3%，為表現最強道指成份股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中東局勢不穩，美國航空及聯合航空分別暫停來往多哈和杜拜的航班，股價分別升0.4%及跌不足0.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/bplib_20250417-111635_20250317_GL_Apple-Watch-10_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/bplib_20250417-111635_20250317_GL_Apple-Watch-10_source-ap__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
