        {
            "title": "佰澤醫療暗盤早段升約28%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">佰澤醫療(02609)暗盤大升，曾升近三成，現升約28%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"佰澤醫療官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/Bayzed-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"佰澤醫療官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/Bayzed-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">佰澤醫療官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立暗盤最高見5.44元，較招股價4.22元高28.91%，最低報4.5元，升6.64%。現升28.67%，報5.43元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">耀才暗盤最高見5.62元，升33.18%，最低見4.25元，升0.71%。現升25.12%，報5.28元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">致富暗盤最高見5.75元，升36.26%，最低報4.52元，升7.11%，現升28.2%，報5.41元。</p>\n</div>",
